Problem-First vs. Solution-First

The Problem-First Philosophy

The traditional, rigorous approach. Don't use a hammer for a screw. If you're optimizing airline schedules, you need Operations Research (OR), not just a chatbot.

The Solution-First Spark

GenAI inspires new possibilities. Explore what problems can be solved by its ability to interpret unstructured data and explain complex concepts.

Hybrid Harmony

"The consensus? LLMs translate human problems into precise mathematical models, while Agentic AI orchestrates the workflows."
